     H            Y.
      ** UEXR55A****************************************************
      *  CHECK LABEL BY PACKING LIST#  IF IT PRINTED BEFORE        *
      *  JW     2025.01.21                                         *
      **************************************************************
      *  CALLING SEQ.
      *                    CALL 'UEXR55A'
      *                    PARM           $BARC   9
      *                    PARM           $STT    1
      * IN   $BARC    9A  PACKING LIST#
      * IN   $STT     1A  STATUS (Y=PRINTED BEFORE, N=NOT PRINTED
      *==========================================================
     FAB#XL01DIF  E           K        DISK
      *==========================================================
      ** MAIN ROUTINE
      *==========================================================
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $PL#    9        IN
     C                     PARM           $STT    1        OUT
      *
      * CHECK LABEL TRANSACTION
     C           $PL#      CHAINAB#XL01D             98
     C   98                MOVE 'N'       $STT
     C  N98                MOVE 'Y'       $STT
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
